How to edit the patient’s picture? 1: When logging in this software for the first time, please register an Admin account firstly. Because the Admin account is default, you only need to fill in the password, then fill in the email and your hospital and department, and then click [Save] 2: When registering an ordinary user, you only need to fill in the account number and password and email to complete the registration 1: Click [Register Query] on the patient information interface to go to the query condition interface 2: If you need to query all the patient information under the account name, click [Query] directly; if you need to query specific patient information, you can enter the query conditions, click [Query] (the query condition do not so accurate, specific information can be entered, and patient information containing this condition under the account name will be fully queried.) 3: Admin users can query all patient information without generating a report. Ordinary users can only query patient information that does not generate a report under their name 1: At the image acquisition interface, click the Modify button of queried digital electronic colposcope, as shown in the red circle marker 2:Enter the device name in the dialog box that pops up. Click OK when done 1: At the image acquisition interface, click the Delete button of queried digital electronic colposcope, as shown in the red circle marker 2: device information is cleared after clicking the button, if you need to re-connect the digital electronic colposcope, click on the search button in the upper right corner (need to have a patient not having a generated report) 1: Try to set the WIFI of the digital electronic colposcope in the system setting again, [System Settings] -> [WIFI Settings] 2: After saving WIFI, go to the image acquisition interface to search for digital electronic colposcope 3: If you fail to connect the digital video colposcope after the first two steps, try to restart the software 1 : If it fails to generate a PDF report during the process of generating a report, you can click [Menu] ->[Modify Report] -> select the PDF report, and then modify the PDF report and click to generate report 1 : Select [Medical History Management] -> enter the query conditions (conditions can be empty), and then click [Query] -> directly click on the patient you need to view, and then display the patient’s medical record information 1 : Select [Medical History Management] -> enter the query conditions (conditions can be empty), and then click [Query] 2 : Select two medical records you want to compare, and then click one of the selected medical records 1 : one-key clear connected digital electronic colposcope;
